          "alternative-color": true,
          "image": "shopify://shop_images/Riehle_s_labor_day_specials.005.jpeg",
          "title": "Indiana Grown Gourmet Popcorn",
          "description": "<p>Riehle’s Select Gourmet Popcorn is a family owned, family run popcorn company rooted in the rich farmland of southeastern Indiana. We plant, harvest, clean, and pack our kernels on our farm in the Midwest, then ship them fresh to your door across the United States. Our lineup features tender hulless options, classic white and yellow gourmet popcorn, and specialty kernels prized for big, fluffy flakes and dependable popping performance.<br/><br/>Whether you use a stovetop popper, air popper, or electric popcorn machine, you can count on light, crisp texture and full flavor in every bowl. Shop by popcorn type and kernel size, add popping oils and seasonings, or stock up with bulk and wholesale cases for events, fundraisers, offices, and concession stands. Farm fresh quality, friendly service, and consistent results make Riehle’s a favorite for movie night and everyday snacking.</p>",
          "link-url": "shopify://pages/about-us",
          "link-text": "Learn More About Us"
        }
      },
