          "background-color": "light",
          "heading": "Riehle's Select Popcorn",
          "text": "<p>Riehle’s Select Gourmet Popcorn is a family owned Indiana popcorn company growing, cleaning, and packing premium kernels on our farm. Explore tender hulless, classic white and yellow, and specialty varieties, plus popping oils, seasonings, and poppers for perfect results at home. Enjoy fresh, non-GMO gourmet popcorn shipped nationwide, with bulk and gift options ready for movie night, events, and everyday snacking.</p>"
